title: The psychology of narcissism - W. Keith Campbell
description: Narcissism isn’t just a personality type that shows up in advice columns; it’s actually a set of traits classified and studied by psychologists. But what causes it? And can narcissists improve on their negative traits? W. Keith Campbell describes the psychology behind the elevated and sometimes detrimental self-involvement of narcissists.

title: Physical and Mental Health
description: A clear distinction is often made between “mind” and “body” – but mental health and physical health should not be thought of as separate. Learn more about the link between physical health and mental health.

title: How to Heal Anxious Attachment - Fast!
description: Feeling anxious or overwhelmed in your relationships? You’re not alone. This video explores steps to heal anxious attachment and build secure, healthier relationships. Learn tools like recognizing your triggers and practicing self-soothing.

title: What is Mindfulness?
description: Mindfulness is the practice of acknowledging your feelings without judgment. Discover why mindfulness matters and how you can benefit from it.

title: Mental Health: How the Brain Works
description: This 3D animation shows brain regions tied to mental health. Learn how neurons communicate and explore examples of mental illnesses and their related neurotransmitters.

title: 8 Things You Can Do To Improve Your Mental Health
description: Wondering how to boost your mental health? This video offers 8 healthy habits that can make a lasting difference if you stick with them. Improve your well-being with these practical tips.

title: 8 Ways to Become More Emotionally Mature
description: What does it mean to be emotionally mature? Learn the qualities of emotionally mature people and discover 8 ways to strengthen your emotional intelligence and resilience.

title: How To Practice Self Love
description: Self love goes beyond appearance or possessions—it’s about valuing yourself emotionally and spiritually. Learn four core elements of self love and practical steps for building it over time.
